          "label": "Ivabradine",
          "type": "EXPERIMENTAL",
          "description": "Ivabradine: initial dose of 5 mg b.id. dose up-titration to 7,5 mg b.id. in 2 weeks due to the heart rate and maintaining the last dose during 6 months.",
